<refnamediv>
	<refname>vfs_full_audit</refname>
	<refpurpose>record Samba VFS operations in the system log</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
	<cmdsynopsis sepchar=" ">
		<literal>vfs objects = full_audit</literal>
	</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1>
	<title>DESCRIPTION</title>

	<para>This VFS module is part of the
	<citerefentry><refentrytitle>samba</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>7</manvolnum></citerefentry> suite.</para>

	<para>The <literal>vfs_full_audit</literal> VFS module records selected
	client operations to the system log using
	<citerefentry><refentrytitle>syslog</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>3</manvolnum></citerefentry>.</para>

	<para><literal>vfs_full_audit</literal> is able to record the
